OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777341846
OL,3,CFuel subsidy scheme for farmers to be
OL,4,Cbrought to Cabinet
OL,6,FA 100 million-euro fuel subsidy scheme
OL,7,Ffor farmers that will see payments
OL,8,Fbackdated to March is to go before
OL,9,FCabinet on Tuesday.
OL,11,FAgriculture Minister Martin Heydon has
OL,12,Fsaid the savings from the scheme,
OL,13,Fcombined with previous measures
OL,14,Fannounced by the Government, will
OL,15,Freduce green diesel by 27.4 cent per
OL,16,Flitre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
