FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777341846
OL,3,CFuel subsidy scheme for farmers to be
OL,4,Cbrought to Cabinet
OL,6,FThe subsidy scheme is part of the 505
OL,7,Fmillion-euro package announced by the
OL,8,FGovernment in the wake of fuel
OL,9,Fprotests and blockades that saw fuel
OL,10,Fsupplies limited across the country.
OL,12,FIt was unveiled less than three weeks
OL,13,Fafter 250 million euro (#218 million)
OL,14,Fworth of measures were announced by
OL,15,Fgovernment responding to the fuel
OL,16,Fcrisis sparked by the war in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777341846
OL,3,CFuel subsidy scheme for farmers to be
OL,4,Cbrought to Cabinet
OL,6,FConstruction contractors, quarry truck
OL,7,Fdrivers and others driving vehicles
OL,8,Fdeemed essential for construction are
OL,9,Fto be added to those who qualify for
OL,10,Fthe package of fuel supports,
OL,11,Ffollowing the leaders' meeting on
OL,12,FMonday.
OL,14,FThe whole fuel support package is
OL,15,Fexpected to be finalised in the coming
OL,16,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
