FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777341846
OL,3,CFuel subsidy scheme for farmers to be
OL,4,Cbrought to Cabinet
OL,6,FThe subsidy scheme aims to assist farm
OL,7,Fcontractors, farmers and fishers who
OL,8,Fhave been severely impacted by the
OL,9,Fincreased costs of fuel since the
OL,10,Fstart of the war in Iran and the
OL,11,Feffective shutdown of vital trading
OL,12,Froute the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,14,FAs a result, the price of marked gas
OL,15,Foil (MGO), also known as green diesel,
OL,16,Fhas almost doubled since February.
OL,18,FMGO cost 97 cent per litre in late
OL,19,FFebruary, rising to 1.70 euro per
OL,20,Flitre by late March and is now at 1.80
OL,21,Feuro per litre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777341846
OL,3,CFuel subsidy scheme for farmers to be
OL,4,Cbrought to Cabinet
OL,6,FThe 100 million-euro Fuel Subsidy
OL,7,FSupport Scheme, which includes 15
OL,8,Fmillion euro for fisheries and
OL,9,Faquaculture, will see payments
OL,10,Fcovering the months from March to
OL,11,FJuly, which is the busiest period for
OL,12,Ffuel usage on farms.
OL,14,FIt is understood that around 120,000
OL,15,Ffarmers and 1,500 full-time
OL,16,Fagricultural contractors will be
OL,17,Feligible for the payments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777341846
OL,3,CFuel subsidy scheme for farmers to be
OL,4,Cbrought to Cabinet
OL,6,FTo use the scheme, applicants will
OL,7,Fneed to apply online and the size of
OL,8,Fthe payments will be based on their
OL,9,Ffuel usage in 2025.
OL,11,FMr Heydon said previously that the
OL,12,Fpackage for farmers was one he had
OL,13,Fbeen working on "for some time".
OL,15,FHe said the initial 250 million-euro
OL,16,Fpackage of supports from Government
OL,17,Flimited action on green diesel because
OL,18,Fwhile it had risen exponentially as a
OL,19,Fresult of the war in the Middle East,
OL,20,Fthere is "very little" excise on it.
OL,26,@uD@QOUuD@_O]|D@JOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777341846
OL,3,CFuel subsidy scheme for farmers to be
OL,4,Cbrought to Cabinet
OL,6,F"So what I was doing was designing the
OL,7,Fscheme over the Easter break, before
OL,8,Fthe protests ever started," he told
OL,9,FRTE's Today With David McCullagh
OL,10,Fprogramme.
OL,12,F"I had meetings in Government
OL,13,FBuildings on Holy Week with the farm
OL,14,Fcontractors of Ireland, with the IFA
OL,15,F(Irish Farmers' Association) and
OL,16,Fothers around designing the scheme,
OL,17,Fwhich is the first time ever (we) will
OL,18,Fhave had a scheme for our contractors
OL,19,Fdirectly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@[O]tD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777341846
OL,3,CFuel subsidy scheme for farmers to be
OL,4,Cbrought to Cabinet
OL,6,FHe said the subsidy payments would be
OL,7,Fbackdated to March 1 and cover the
OL,8,Ffive-month period from March through
OL,9,Fto July, covering the busy farming
OL,10,Fperiod including from the silage
OL,11,Fseason and the cereals harvesting
OL,12,Fseason.
OL,14,F"We had contractors who were seeing a
OL,15,F70,000-80,000 euro increase on their
OL,16,Fdiesel bill alone and fear of it not
OL,17,Fbeing sustainable to carry that debt,
OL,18,Fbut farmers not being in a position to
OL,19,Fbe able to pay them," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777341846
OL,3,CFuel subsidy scheme for farmers to be
OL,4,Cbrought to Cabinet
OL,6,FHe said the scheme would provide a
OL,7,Flump-sum payment based on an
OL,8,Fapplication where applicants self-
OL,9,Fdeclare their fuel usage for last year.
OL,11,FHe said there will be caps and
OL,12,Fceilings in place that would be agreed
OL,13,Fwith farm contractor representatives
OL,14,Fand that he had also discussed the
OL,15,Fmatter with the banks "to allow for
OL,16,Fthe fact that this money is coming".
OL,18,F"I will do this as quickly as
OL,19,Fpossible," he said.
OL,26,@wD@WOUxD@cO]zD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
